WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.508 --> 00:00:13.421
<b>I wake up at night
feeling thirsty.</b>

2
00:00:13.811 --> 00:00:16.046
<b>I want to get some water.</b>

3
00:00:16.311 --> 00:00:20.046
<b>I start looking for my slippers
under the bed.</b>

4
00:00:20.781 --> 00:00:24.812
<b>Oh my God!
There is a tiger under my bed.</b>

5
00:00:27.265 --> 00:00:29.453
<b>Now what should I do?</b>

6
00:00:29.961 --> 00:00:31.632
<b>Should I call Ma?</b>

7
00:00:32.148 --> 00:00:34.304
<b>What if the tiger roars?</b>

8
00:00:36.921 --> 00:00:39.789
<b>Should I just go back to sleep?</b>

9
00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:42.679
<b>But I am not sleepy any more.</b>

10
00:00:42.961 --> 00:00:48.375
<b>Then someone turns on the light</b>

11
00:00:49.032 --> 00:00:51.179
<b>Ma is standing at the door.</b>

12
00:00:51.812 --> 00:00:55.625
<b>What happened dear?
Did you call me?</b>

13
00:00:56.094 --> 00:00:57.117
<b>asks Ma.</b>

14
00:00:57.742 --> 00:01:01.351
<b>I point towards the tiger.</b>

15
00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:07.765
<b>Ma bends and pulls the tiger out
 from under the bed!</b>

16
00:01:08.531 --> 00:01:11.757
<b>Hey, this is no tiger.</b>

17
00:01:12.578 --> 00:01:17.289
<b>This is my thick yellow
and black sweater.</b>

18
00:01:17.968 --> 00:01:21.359
<b>Its buttons shine like
a tiger's eyes.</b>

19
00:01:22.062 --> 00:01:25.289
<b>I got scared for nothing!</b>

20
00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:28.148
<b>Ma gets me some water.</b>

21
00:01:29.461 --> 00:01:32.007
<b>Now I will sleep.</b>

22
00:01:32.671 --> 00:01:37.867
<b>And dream about real
tigers in a jungle!</b>

